    <description>A MonoGame library that emulates old-school console and command prompt style graphics.</description>
    <releaseNotes>Initial release. The other libraries (SadConsole.Ansi, SadConsle.Controls, SadConsole.GameHelpers) have merged into a single library, SadConsole.dll
    
Rewrite and refactor of code.

Single NuGet package that will contain all platform targets.</releaseNotes>
    <copyright>Copyright 2017 Steve De George JR</copyright>
    <tags>monogame roguelike cli xna game development console ansi ascii</tags>
